THE NEW HYMN AND TUNE BOOK.
A COLLECTION
OF
HYMNS AND TUNES
FOR
PUBLIC, SOCIAL, AND DOMESTIC
WORSHIP.
Sing praises to God, sing praises.-PSALM xlvii. 6.
There are no songs comparable to the songs of Zion.-MILTON.
NASHVILLE, TENN.:
SOUTHERN METHODIST PUBLISHING HOUSE.
1880.
